 7 │
 8 │ [target."cuda-*".dependencies]
   ·          ───┬──
   ·             ╰── target selector specified here
 9 │ foo = "1.0"
   ╰────
  help: Declare a platform whose name matches 'cuda-*', using `pixi workspace platform add <name>`
